rComments: Easy class. Teacher is totally hot! Loved going just to see him. :)...class is ok. Gets a bit boring at times. Group project is ok, final paper is 10 pages, which is pointless. Paper was the only thing I did not like. Overall not a horrible class.

Horrible class. Wish I had dropped it when I had the chance. Gives avg of 100 pgs of weekly reading and tests on it. Final project consisted of 14 pg group paper, 10 pg individual paper, a class presentation, all on top of a CUMULATIVE FINAL. Worked harder for this 3 hour class than the 7 hours of 300/400 classes I was taking. Just awful. Avoid.
